<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ShadowMods Pro | Dashboard</title>
    <link
      rel="icon"
      href="https://i.postimg.cc/y87h3x7y/0dc15569002a714e09ef3b03da9ac43d-removebg-preview.png"
      type="image/x-icon"
    />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        background-color: #121212;
        color: #e0e0e0;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-image: url("https://i.postimg.cc/y87h3x7y/0dc15569002a714e09ef3b03da9ac43d-removebg-preview.png");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        position: relative;
      }

      body::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        z-index: -1;
      }

      nav {
        position: absolute;
        top: 20px;
        right: 20px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      nav a {
        color: #00bcd4;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-left: 15px;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
      }

      nav a:hover {
        color: #0097a7;
      }

      .content {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: 800px;
      }

      h1 {
        color: #00bcd4;
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .text-section {
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      footer {
        margin-top: 40px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #e0e0e0;
      }

      @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
        .content {
          padding: 15px;
        }
        .text-section {
          padding: 15px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
      <a href="/install">Install</a>
      <a href="/commands">Commands</a>
      <a href="/help">Help</a>
      <a href="/status">Status</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="content">
      <h1>Welcome to the Bot Dashboard</h1>
      <p>Manage your bot, commands, and settings from here!</p>

      <div class="text-section">
        <p>
          ShadowMods Pro offers a comprehensive suite of tools for Discord management, custom bot creation, and modding solutions. Our goal is to provide powerful and user-friendly features that enhance your experience while maintaining the highest levels of security and performance.
        </p>
        <p>
          From logging and analytics to custom commands and integrations, ShadowMods Pro ensures that you have the tools you need to succeed. Explore our features, check the bot status, and make the most of your ShadowMods Pro experience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer>&copy; 2024 ShadowMods Pro. All rights reserved.</footer>
  </body>
</html>
